<p>These coordinates have an elegant description in terms of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quaternion" title="Quaternion">quaternions</a>. Any unit quaternion <span class="texhtml mvar" style="font-style:italic;">q</span> can be written as a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Versor" title="Versor">versor</a>:
