<p>where <span class="texhtml"><b>v</b> = (<i>v</i><sub>1</sub>, <i>v</i><sub>2</sub>, <i>v</i><sub>3</sub>)</span> is another vector in <span class="texhtml"><b>R</b><sup>3</sup></span>. The inverse of this map takes <span class="texhtml mvar" style="font-style:italic;">p</span> to
